        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Begins a write request for the specified attribute and returns a buffer into which the app should write the data before calling smartstrap_attribute_end_write. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>The buffer must not be used after smartstrap_attribute_end_write is called. </para>
