</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="out">buffer_length</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The length of the buffer in bytes. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para><computeroutput>SmartstrapResultOk</computeroutput> if a write operation was started and the <computeroutput>buffer</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>buffer_length</computeroutput> parameters were set, or an error otherwise. </para>
